{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Rainbow cauliflower sushi","content":["Place cauliflower into mixing bowl and chop <b>8 sec\/\/speed 5<b>, mixing with aid of spatula. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place cashews into mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 7<b>.","Add avocado, sesame oil and wasabi and blend <b>6 sec\/speed 10<b>.","Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and blend for a further <b>6 sec\/speed 10<b>. Transfer into a bowl, then clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place 1 nori sheet, shiny side down, onto a bamboo sushi mat. Spread 6 compacted tablespoons of the reserved cauliflower over the bottom two-thirds of the nori sheet, leaving top one-third free. Spread 1 heaped tablespoon of the avocado mixture in a line across cauliflower at the end closest to you. Layer 4 pieces of the capsicum, 4 pieces of the cabbage and 4 pieces of the spring onions\/shallots onto avocado mixture. Brush the top edge of nori sheet with water. Using the bamboo sushi mat, begin rolling tightly from the bottom up to form a roll. Allow to sit for 1-2 minutes, seam side down, then slice into 6 pieces. Repeat with remaining nori sheets, cauliflower, avocado mixture and vegetables (makes 6 rolls in total)."]},{"title":"Peanut dipping sauce","content":["Place peanuts into mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then transfer 2 teaspoons of the chopped peanuts into a small bowl and set aside.","Add water, syrup, tamari and Sriracha® and blend <b>1 min\/speed 10<b>. Transfer into a small dipping bowl, sprinkle with reserved chopped peanuts and serve with sushi."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Rainbow cauliflower sushi","content":["530 g cauliflower, cut into pieces (3 cm)","50 g raw cashews","1 avocado, flesh only","1 tsp sesame oil","1 ½ tsp wasabi paste","6 nori sheets","½ red capsicum, cut into fine julienne","50 g red cabbage, shredded","1 - 2 spring onions\/shallots, cut into fine julienne","filtered water, for brushing"]},{"title":"Peanut dipping sauce","content":["100 g roasted unsalted peanuts","1 - 2 tbsp filtered water","1 - 2 tbsp pure maple syrup","1 - 2 tbsp tamari, gluten free (see Tip)","3 - 4 tsp Sriracha® sauce"]}],"id":"r341217","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-wlwvXOQmOn0\/XZam9VDs47I\/AAAAAAAAg4A\/d2OdyST_7ZMJkzgZhA1BvX3CWrx7rX1BgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_-Zyo3cENxriCeLbn.png","title":"Rainbow cauliflower sushi","publishedAt":"2016-08-01T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"10.1 g","fat":"21.1 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"13.3 g","calories":"1230.3 kJ \/ 292.9 kcal"},"usefulItems":"small bowl, bowl, bamboo sushi mat, pastry brush","hintsAndTricks":["Be sure to check the label of your tamari, as not all brands are gluten free."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","50m","6 portions"]}